00:53:41,530 --> 00:53:43,030
Tell them the truth.

784
00:53:54,170 --> 00:53:55,210
Yes.

785
00:53:58,300 --> 00:53:59,340
At that moment,

786
00:54:02,970 --> 00:54:04,010
I was scared,

787
00:54:08,060 --> 00:54:09,100
afraid,

788
00:54:13,900 --> 00:54:15,060
and flustered.

789
00:54:21,240 --> 00:54:22,280
In that situation,

790
00:54:24,200 --> 00:54:26,200
my mentor, Lieutenant Oh, was hurt,

791
00:54:29,370 --> 00:54:31,500
and the victim was bleeding.

792
00:54:33,960 --> 00:54:35,040
All I could think of

793
00:54:38,130 --> 00:54:39,960
was that I had to save them both.

794
00:54:40,050 --> 00:54:43,340
Then Officer Yeom,
your mind was very clear.

795
00:54:45,930 --> 00:54:49,140
You wanted to save the innocent.

796
00:54:51,270 --> 00:54:52,350
Next.

797
00:54:52,480 --> 00:54:54,190
-Officer Yeom--
-Officer Jang.

798
00:54:54,890 --> 00:54:56,310
Give me a chance to speak.

799
00:54:58,570 --> 00:55:00,020
There are many errors

800
00:55:01,150 --> 00:55:02,610
