852
00:57:45,320 --> 00:57:47,400
<i>When their colleagues and the public</i>

853
00:57:47,480 --> 00:57:49,360
<i>are fighting for their lives,</i>

854
00:57:49,440 --> 00:57:51,280
<i>must they still memorize</i>

855
00:57:51,360 --> 00:57:54,280
<i>and stick to the manual every single time?</i>

856
00:57:54,700 --> 00:57:56,370
How many people here

857
00:57:57,080 --> 00:57:59,750
