858
00:58:01,460 --> 00:58:03,580
None of us can do that.

859
00:58:04,080 --> 00:58:06,130
So why do we expect and demand

860
00:58:06,290 --> 00:58:08,210
an officer stay calm and clear-headed

861
00:58:08,300 --> 00:58:11,840
