897
01:01:30,420 --> 01:01:32,460
Have a sense of duty.

898
01:01:33,790 --> 01:01:35,250
In any situation,

899
01:01:36,840 --> 01:01:38,550
always put

900
01:01:39,920 --> 01:01:43,340
