1047
01:12:28,610 --> 01:12:30,410
-Won-u, let's hurry.
-Yes, sir.

1048
01:12:30,490 --> 01:12:33,660
Code Two. At Namgyeong Chinese Restaurant
on Somyeong 1-gil, the owner

1049
01:12:33,740 --> 01:12:35,750
and a customer are arguing
due to a dine-and-dash.

1050
01:12:35,830 --> 01:12:39,080
Patrol cars in the vicinity,
please report.

1051
01:12:39,170 --> 01:12:40,790
-We're here.
-You're so dead.

1052
01:12:41,290 --> 01:12:42,500
Let's find out who's at fault.

1053
01:12:42,590 --> 01:12:45,340
Officer! Please go by the law
and punish the one who's at fault.

1054
01:12:45,420 --> 01:12:48,130
-What's the matter, sir?
-This prick punched me in the face.

1055
01:12:48,220 --> 01:12:51,050
You piece of shit.
You spat at me as I was walking by.

1056
01:12:51,140 --> 01:12:53,010
Gosh,
what are you guys doing here right now?

1057
01:12:53,100 --> 01:12:55,310
Jeez, enough! Break it up.

1058
01:12:55,390 --> 01:12:57,680
-Please have a seat.
-Gosh, don't!

1059
01:12:58,310 --> 01:13:00,600
Stay right there.
Calm down, or I'm going to lock you up.

1060
01:13:14,830 --> 01:13:21,830
TRAFFIC ENFORCEMENT

1061
01:15:02,270 --> 01:15:03,270
Salute.

1062
01:15:03,440 --> 01:15:07,230
We're on our way back to the station,
but I told him to pull over for a moment

1063
01:15:07,310 --> 01:15:08,940
because I wanted to meet you.

1064
01:15:09,150 --> 01:15:10,780
-It's nice to meet you.
-Likewise.

1065
01:15:11,690 --> 01:15:12,820
You must be stressed out

1066
01:15:12,950 --> 01:15:14,240
because of that dude.

1067
01:15:15,820 --> 01:15:16,740
Yes.

1068
01:15:17,660 --> 01:15:19,530
-I need to buy cigarettes.
-Okay.

1069
01:15:22,540 --> 01:15:23,660
Lieutenant, you transferred

1070
01:15:23,750 --> 01:15:26,120
to Traffic Services to take it easy
after your rehabilitation.

1071
01:15:27,380 --> 01:15:29,380
But I heard that you're

1072
01:15:29,540 --> 01:15:30,590
swamped all the time.

1073
01:15:31,170 --> 01:15:32,420
I totally am.

1074
01:15:32,510 --> 01:15:35,840
I shouldn't have transferred
to Traffic Services.

1075
01:15:36,220 --> 01:15:39,890
What's wrong with this area?
So many hit-and-runs happen here.

1076
01:15:40,470 --> 01:15:43,680
It happens less than once a month
in other areas,

1077
01:15:43,810 --> 01:15:46,900
but a hit-and-run or a DUI accident
happens every three days here.

1078
01:15:48,060 --> 01:15:50,230
I also have to put up with fine dust
and exhaust fumes.

1079
01:15:50,820 --> 01:15:51,730
This job is so tough.

1080
01:15:54,780 --> 01:15:55,610
Have I aged?

1081
01:15:57,320 --> 01:15:58,870
Other officers say

1082
01:16:00,490 --> 01:16:02,120
that you're just damn unlucky.

1083
01:16:02,870 --> 01:16:04,830
Why you little...

1084
01:16:07,830 --> 01:16:10,460
By the way, what's your new mentor like?

1085
01:16:10,540 --> 01:16:13,460
He's a total slacker.
He's easy to work with.

1086
01:16:14,630 --> 01:16:16,380
But I'm making his life difficult

1087
01:16:16,470 --> 01:16:18,220
by responding to all sorts of cases.

1088
01:16:20,510 --> 01:16:23,310
A mentee is training his mentor?

1089
01:16:23,810 --> 01:16:24,770
You idiot.

1090
01:16:26,270 --> 01:16:27,810
When will you return to the division?

1091
01:16:27,890 --> 01:16:29,100
I won't go back.

1092
01:16:29,560 --> 01:16:32,190
I only want cushy positions from now on.

1093
01:16:34,280 --> 01:16:36,150
Shall I go to the countryside
like Chief Ki did?

1094
01:16:36,240 --> 01:16:39,200
I heard there are thieves that steal
chili peppers and potatoes.

1095
01:16:39,280 --> 01:16:41,660
Gosh, that's nuts.

1096
01:16:41,740 --> 01:16:44,950
Then I'll think that you'll be back
after your six months here is up.

1097
01:16:48,790 --> 01:16:50,000
Shall we go to Violent Crimes?

1098
01:16:51,750 --> 01:16:54,300
I mean, we're cops.
We might as well be fearless.

1099
01:16:54,550 --> 01:16:57,550
I can go anywhere if it's with you, sir!

1100
01:16:59,050 --> 01:17:00,180
Great!

1101
01:17:00,800 --> 01:17:03,100
Then behave yourself
and don't cause any trouble.

1102
01:17:03,180 --> 01:17:04,390
I'll see you there.

1103
01:17:04,510 --> 01:17:05,850
-Yes, sir!
-Now, go.

1104
01:17:06,730 --> 01:17:07,930
Take it easy, sir.

